{
  "page": "Hardhand",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Hardhand</b></i> is an <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> longship and part of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Fleet\" title=\"Iron Fleet\">Iron Fleet</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is presumably <a href=\"/index.php/Named_after\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Named after\">named after</a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Harwyn_Hoare\" title=\"Harwyn Hoare\">Harwyn Hoare</a> who was known as \"Harwyn Hardhand\" and \"the Hardhand\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hardhand&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hardhand&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><i>Hardhand</i> is among the ships which sail to <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Wyk\" title=\"Old Wyk\">Old Wyk</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot\" title=\"Kingsmoot\">kingsmoot</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <i>Hardhand</i> later sinks after the <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_the_Shields\" title=\"Taking of the Shields\">taking of the Shields</a> when it is dragged under by a ship it had rammed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hardhand&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_29\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 29\">Chapter 29</a>, The Reaver.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands: The Black Blood.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 18\">Chapter 18</a>, The Iron Captain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403145235\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.031 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.054 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 382/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8677/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1382/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 249/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1867/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.52 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   47.333      1 -total\n 69.16%   32.737      1 Template:Italic_title\n 22.73%   10.758      4 Template:Ref\n 14.00%    6.627      4 Template:Ref/core\n  7.19%    3.404      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5444-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403145235 and revision id 263624\n -->\n",
